OL,3,CMeet the Welsh popstar using her music
OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,FWhen I sat down with Twst (her real
OL,7,Fname being Chloe Davis) before her
OL,8,Fheadline set, you couldn't help but
OL,9,Ffall for her charm and genuine
OL,10,Fexcitement to be doing what she loves
OL,11,Fthe most, which is making music and
OL,12,Fperforming to her fans.
OL,14,FYou sometimes hear about those
OL,15,Funbelievable stories that led young
OL,16,Fartists on their path into the music
OL,17,Findustry, well Twst's story is one of
OL,18,Fthem.
