OL,3,CMeet the Welsh popstar using her music
OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,FIt all started with her decision to
OL,7,Fmove out of her childhood home in
OL,8,FBarry at the age of 14, to live in an
OL,9,Fabandoned recording studio in
OL,10,FBlackwood, and learn her craft.
OL,12,FTwst (her real name being Chloe Davis)
OL,13,Fsaid: "There was this old abandoned
OL,14,Frecording studio. I mean, it's a long
OL,15,Fstory, but essentially the guy who
OL,16,Fowned it wanted to make his son the
OL,17,Fnext Justin Bieber.
OL,26,@tD@_rr
