OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F469A1708503979
OL,3,CMeet the Welsh popstar using her music
OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,F"And he really believed that he was
OL,7,Fgoing to be that. So I sort of just
OL,8,Fbummed around the studio while he was
OL,9,Ftrying to become the next Justin
OL,10,FBieber. And I just lived there for a
OL,11,Fwhile. It was crazy."
OL,13,FTwst also spoke about how this period
OL,14,Fin her life has influenced the music
OL,15,Fshe makes today.
OL,17,FShe said: "I always create from that
OL,18,Fperiod. I think I create from that
OL,19,Fspace that I created for myself when I
OL,20,Fwas that age."
