OL,3,CMeet the Welsh popstar using her music
OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,F"I feel I was very much exploring
OL,7,Fthese worlds inside my head because I
OL,8,Fwas very isolated there as well. It
OL,9,Fwas a lot of imagination and educating
OL,10,Fmyself through the internet and
OL,11,Fteaching myself all the things that I
OL,12,Fwanted to know."
OL,14,FTwst says it is important for her to
OL,15,Fuse her music as a form of self-
OL,16,Fexpression and to highlight the
OL,17,Finjustices that exist today. A lot of
OL,18,Fher music refers to the misogyny that
OL,19,Fwomen face in society and the music
OL,20,Findustry in particular.
