OL,3,CMeet the Welsh popstar using her music
OL,4,Cto highlight misogyny in the industry
OL,6,FThat's something that Twst often
OL,7,Frefers to in her songwriting - the
OL,8,Fcomplexities of the modern-day and
OL,9,Fhaving to exist in both the digital
OL,10,Fworld and the real world.
OL,12,FShe described the struggles she has
OL,13,Ffaced in navigating these two
OL,14,Fdifferent worlds as a young female.
OL,16,F"Obviously, I'm just constantly
OL,17,Foverwhelmed, like the whole world is
OL,18,Fand it's like we're not built as
OL,19,Fhumans to be able to keep up with the
OL,20,Fpace of it. I mean, it's challenging,
OL,21,Fright?"
